flowchart LR
  U[Users<br/>web / mobile] --> NW[Network<br/>CDN · firewall · VPN]
  NW --> LB[Load balancer]
  LB --> APP[App / API servers]
  APP --> CA[(Cache)]
  APP --> MS[Model serving<br/>GPU · REST/gRPC]
  MS --> FS[(Feature store<br/>/ database)]
  MS -. prediction logs .-> OS[(Object storage<br/>training data)]
  OS --> TRN[Training pipeline<br/>GPU]
  TRN --> MR[(Model registry)]
  MR -- deploy --> MS

